  "3067260": {
    "name": "Tales from the Mabinogion",
    "steam_appid": 3067260,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067260/extras/f6d0128254de69d0545e6df63ae85c56.poster.avif?t=1765642493\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067260/extras/f6d0128254de69d0545e6df63ae85c56.webm?t=1765642493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067260/extras/f6d0128254de69d0545e6df63ae85c56.mp4?t=1765642493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在血与剑铸就的时代，你将化身普德睿——古老威尔士达费德王国的君主。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当神秘的迷雾来袭，王国的命运，悬于你的抉择之间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《玛比诺吉昂传奇》以全新姿态重现中世纪威尔士的神话故事，带你走进《玛比诺吉昂》的古老传奇之中。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067260/extras/f92678bcd83e00f49a0b3fd291f5d69a.poster.avif?t=1765642493\" width=1170 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067260/extras/f92678bcd83e00f49a0b3fd291f5d69a.webm?t=1765642493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067260/extras/f92678bcd83e00f49a0b3fd291f5d69a.mp4?t=1765642493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从古老的森林到饱受海浪冲刷的海岸，达费德是一片由传说塑造的土地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >循着足迹、符号与流动的迷雾，你将踏入幽暗的林间、荒凉的山岭与被遗忘的废墟。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款以叙事为核心的探索游戏中，你将漫步于这片古老的国度，倾听它的故事，并在旅途中将散落的传说重新连结。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067260/extras/0720780f705ad05878f168e2f32256b2.poster.avif?t=1765642493\" width=1170 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067260/extras/0720780f705ad05878f168e2f32256b2.webm?t=1765642493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067260/extras/0720780f705ad05878f168e2f32256b2.mp4?t=1765642493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的叙事全程以威尔士语呈现，由威尔士诗歌音乐艺术节桂冠得主里斯·约尔沃思（Rhys Iorwerth）亲自改编剧本。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多语字幕让每位玩家都能在聆听神话原声的同时追随故事的脚步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从语言到山海，从声韵到景致，整个体验忠实再现中世纪威尔士的气息，让你在雾与歌的回响中，沉浸于这片传说之地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067260/extras/734017f12b8a5313886696a5c590535d.poster.avif?t=1765642493\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067260/extras/734017f12b8a5313886696a5c590535d.webm?t=1765642493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067260/extras/734017f12b8a5313886696a5c590535d.mp4?t=1765642493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067260/extras/0951df4588bf6f039df01ac4a0200bde.poster.avif?t=1765642493\" width=1170 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067260/extras/0951df4588bf6f039df01ac4a0200bde.webm?t=1765642493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067260/extras/0951df4588bf6f039df01ac4a0200bde.mp4?t=1765642493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>纯正的威尔士语演绎</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全程以威尔士语呈现，由屡获殊荣的配音员菲尔·罗（Phil Rowe）倾情演出，带来最原汁原味的叙事体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>神话般的故事叙述</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入探索《玛比诺吉昂》的古老传说，由《纽约时报》畅销作家加夫·索普（Gav Thorpe）与威尔士国家诗歌音乐艺术节桂冠得主里斯·约尔沃思（Rhys Iorwerth）共同改编，为游戏注入神话色彩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>沉浸式探索体验</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在精心打造的环境中自由徜徉，追寻安温乐土的异兽踪迹，逃离致命的诅咒迷雾，揭开被时光掩埋的古老秘密。漫步于达费德王国的大地，发掘《玛比诺吉昂》书页间尘封千年的传说。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>经验丰富的开发团队</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由斯特万·阿纳斯塔索夫（Stevan Anastasoff） 领衔开发，其代表作包括《刺客信条》、《战锤Online》、《荣耀战魂》。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >团队成员囊括多位获奖作家、音乐家与配音员，共同打造一场跨越神话的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>油画般的视觉氛围</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以独特的着色器技术呈现“油画风”视觉风格，灵感源自文森特·梵高（Vincent Van Gogh）、卡斯帕·大卫·弗里德里希（Caspar David Friedrich）与乔治·英尼斯（George Innes） 的艺术作品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>扣人心弦的音乐体验</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸于威尔士著名民谣音乐家奥利弗·威尔逊-迪克森（Oliver Wilson-Dickson） 的动人旋律中，让音符与传说共鸣，谱写出跨越世纪的神话之歌。</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 威尔士语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 简体中文<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
